latestPosts.caption:
I am beyond honoured. Receiving the Whitley Gold award 2024 signifies victory for the Hargila, a species that has long battled negative perceptions. This award is dedicated to our  people of Assam, who support our work and bless us abundantly. They are the true green warriors, as we reside in biodiversity hotspots. It's also a triumph for every woman, every mother , every young girl . our Assamese women are incredibly strong and courageous. They have the power to turn the impossible into reality.  We just need to realise and believe in ourselve. 

#WhitleyGoldAward 2024
#sharedfuture
